{"tid":2403020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反修例紀錄片《Do Not Split不割席》入圍奧斯卡紀錄短片十強","createTime":"2021-02-11T00:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T00:12:39.000Z","uid":382478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"280420ee61253819178ec1f20a65463961a2739f","tid":2403020,"uid":382478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i03S8.G8d6o4GKFU9vD5Bw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MC4yMTgxODE4MTgxODE4/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/a92bfcb0-6b75-11eb-9ffb-46068f6b6680\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi03S8.G8d6o4GKFU9vD5Bw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MC4yMTgxODE4MTgxODE4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Fa92bfcb0-6b75-11eb-9ffb-46068f6b6680&h=2d1c570c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//奧斯卡公布咗部份獎項初步入圍名單，當中「最佳紀錄短片」獎項嘅十強，包括由挪威製作人Anders Hammer執導、紀錄2019年香港反修例運動嘅作品《Do Not Split不割席》//<br />\n//影片長約35分鐘，紀錄多次示威的街頭情況。本身亦係記者嘅Anders Hammer，走到多個衝突現場，紀錄呢場佢認為係前年國際政治舞台上最重要事件。Anders Hammer喺訪問提到，好難理解抗爭點發生，想知點解一班年青人要咁做，亦喺佢地嘅行動見到獨特之處以及團結。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1lol%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-do-not-split%E4%B8%8D%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E5%8D%81%E5%BC%B7-080827208.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1lol%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587-do-not-split%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%258D%25A1%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25BC%25B7-080827208.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLONdVtVfIexd6qH9